cu.error_type: unreachable elements or wrong routing definitions
cu.explanation_en: Changing the GNB port for S1-U to 2153 instead of 2152 prevents the CU from establishing GTP-U tunnels on the correct port, disrupting user plane connectivity.

du.explanation_en: Setting ul_offstToCarrier to 1 causes uplink carrier frequency offset, resulting in misaligned uplink subcarrier positions and degraded uplink signal quality.
